  %% Diagram 11A: CQRS Event Replay and Read-Model Rebuild Workflow

  Trigger[Replay trigger\nNew projector logic, incident recovery, or backfill]
  Scope[Select replay scope\naggregate type, date range, tenant scope]
  Snapshot[Create safety snapshot of current read models]
  Load[(Load ordered events from event_store)]

  Checkpoint[Replay checkpoint store\nlast_event_id, status, duration]
  Project[Re-run projectors against historical events]
  Build[(Rebuild read models\norders, analytics, notifications, search docs)]
  Cache[Refresh or invalidate Redis caches]
  Validate[Validate rebuilt models\ncounts, checksums, sample queries]

  Cutover{Validation passed?}
  Promote[Promote rebuilt projections to active reads]
  Rollback[Rollback to prior snapshot]
  Alert[Raise incident for manual review]

  Resume{Replay interrupted?}
  ResumeFrom[Resume from checkpoint]

  Trigger --> Scope --> Snapshot --> Load --> Project --> Build --> Cache --> Validate --> Cutover
  Load --> Checkpoint
  Project --> Checkpoint

  Cutover -- Yes --> Promote
  Cutover -- No --> Rollback --> Alert

  Project --> Resume
  Resume -- Yes --> ResumeFrom --> Project
  Resume -- No --> Build
